query:
SELECT
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE locked_at IS NULL AND run_at <= NOW()) as "ready!: i64",
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE locked_at IS NOT NULL) as "running!: i64",
                COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE locked_at IS NULL AND run_at > NOW()) as "scheduled!: i64",
                COUNT(*) as "total!: i64"
            FROM jobs
